title: Warcraft Novels & Comics (Nearly complete)
description:
I'm missing two that I could really use so there's a one-stop torrent for all your Warcraft reading needs:

(Graphic Novel) = Bloodsworn
(Manga) = Shadow Wing - Nexus Point


Outside of those two, everything else (including the latest Vol'jin - Shadow of the Horde) is all there. These were all found through tons of different downloads that are years old, and I felt that since there's new material that there might as well be a new updated library in torrent form.



SUGGESTED PROGRAMS FOR YOUR READING ENJOYMENT:

*CDisplayEX (.cbr files)
*Calibre (.epub & .mobi)







Seed, please. Even if it's only 20KiB/s.
